{"tid":1004229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳橋塌工作台釀2死3公司罰61萬 家屬批判刑太輕","createTime":"2019-02-01T09:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T12:04:16.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d611d8a29e47da8a234c056a8386fbb8058946","tid":1004229,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋‪香港接線一段於前年‬3月29日發生嚴重工業意外，橋底的臨時工作台發生倒塌意外，釀成2死3傷慘劇，事後承建商、監督工程的顧問公司連同多名職員，修訂後被票控35張傳票。涉案3間大判公司各被控9張傳票，早前已認罪，案件今在西九龍法院判刑，裁判官指本案的意外是一齣悲劇，公司有責任提供安全環境予工人，但考慮到即時認罪，3間公司共判罰款61.4萬元。<br />\n<br />\n3間公司分別為香港寶嘉建築有限公司、中國港灣工程有限責任公司，及威勝利香港有限公司。寶嘉被罰26.4萬元、中國港灣被罰款21.4萬元及威勝利被罰13.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示要判處具阻嚇性的刑罰，向社會傳達「保護工人是最為重要」的訊息，亦不認為3間公司因聯營承辦工程，從而可攤分刑罰。事故中喪命的家屬，同樣認為判刑太輕，批評政府未有加重刑罰，同類意外只會再生；另外亦責承辦商只因「趕工」，妄顧工人安全致意外發生。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190201/_2019020115575722067.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190201%2F_2019020115575722067.jpg&h=218c10ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihOWpTosf9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DihOWpTosf9s&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxshd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=3a79eb00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihOWpTosf9s</a>"},{"pid":"569621af6844d4f6802064f84285c7d460d74fad","tid":1004229,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:04:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1424874/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1424874%2F&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxshd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=7fb31263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1424874%2F&h=4cfaf9f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1424874/</a>"}]}